Package sorters

Package, that contains classes for sorting arrays using classic algorithms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoSort
    Type of sorting, that uses classic function from java library.
    BubbleSort
    Abstract class for BubbleType sorters.
    BubbleSortDown
    The relative to BubbleSortUp sorting algorithm, but in this type element go under to the bottom of array.
    BubbleSortUp
    Sorting algorithm that repeatedly steps through the list to be sorted, compares each pair of adjacent items and swaps them if they are in the wrong order.
    ExchangeSort
    The exchange sort is similar to its cousin BubbleSortUp in that it compares elements of the array and swaps those that are out of order.
    MergeSort
    Like QuickSort, Merge Sort is a Divide and Conquer algorithm.
    QuickSort
    Like MergeSort QuickSort is a Divide and Conquer algorithm.
    Sort
    Abstract class for sorting array in different ways.
